[gd_scene load_steps=19 format=3]

; M6-C chashitsu (2026-04-22) — primitive-based approximation of the
; 6×6 m tea room produced by erre-sandbox-blender/scripts/export_chashitsu.py.
; The Blender-produced .glb supersedes this primitive build when present at
; res://assets/environment/chashitsu_v1.glb. Until that export lands, the
; primitives below give the researcher the scale and silhouette the user
; requested ("茶室をもう少し大きく / デザイン多様性を持たせたい").
;
; Slice γ (2026-04-25): scene root moved from (0, 0, 15) to
; (33.33, 0, -33.33) to match ``ZONE_CENTERS[CHASHITSU]`` in
; ``src/erre_sandbox/world/zones.py`` (``+WORLD_SIZE_M / 3`` on X,
; ``-WORLD_SIZE_M / 3`` on Z). Child mesh positions are relative and stay
; unchanged. The earlier Z=15 sat outside any zone Voronoi cell, so the
; tea-room visually drifted away from BoundaryLayer's chashitsu rect.

